T01TD1155E:196a-1: gu na aa paryanta sto tram /
T01TD1155E:196a-3: yon tan mtha' yas par bstod pa /
T01TD1155E:196a-4: thams cad mkhyen pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1155E:196a-5: rgyal ba'i yon tan mtha' mi 'tshal bas gal te khyod bsngags mi brjod na //
T01TD1155E:196a-6: 'ga' yang khyod bstod mi bgyid khyod kyi 'byor ba 'gro bas rtogs ma mchis //
T01TD1155E:196a-7: gang slad 'gro 'dis khyod la bstod pa bgyis kyang nongs pa ma mchis pa //
T01TD1155E:196a-8: de slad don 'dir bdag ni blo gros rab tu chung yang brtson pa lags //
T01TD1155E:196b-0: srid gsum dag la phan brtson blo @196b mnga' ngan song gnas na'ang bsngags par 'os //
T01TD1155E:196b-1: rang don smon pa'i blo gros can ni mya ngan 'das kyang ma lags zhes //
T01TD1155E:196b-2: de slad khyod ni 'khor ba'i 'jigs pas mi ldog brtan zhing mi g-yo bas //
T01TD1155E:196b-3: 'jig rten skye zhing 'chi bas nyam thag yongs su bskyab par brtson pa lags //
T01TD1155E:196b-4: srid pa'i 'gro ba dag tu sdug bsngal rnams kyis smas pa'i sems can la //
T01TD1155E:196b-5: bdag gi blo gros rtsub pos sdug bsngal rnam mang de dang de bsgrubs pas //
T01TD1155E:196b-6: de phyir bdag gis de dag rnams la bde ba bskyed phyir bzod bya zhes //
T01TD1155E:196b-7: de slad khyod ni 'gro la zhi ba'i bde ba bskyed slad brtson pa lags //
T01TD1155E:196b-8: sems can gang dag ma rig ldongs pas bsam pa rgud pa'i blo gros can //
T01TD1155E:196b-9: pha dang bur gyur rnams kyis bdag la gnyen snyam byams pas phan btags pa //
T01TD1155E:196b-10: de dag btang nas gcig pu thar par byed pa bdag gi tshul min zhes //
T01TD1155E:196b-11: de slad khyod kyis 'gro ba mgon med nges thar bgyi slad smon lam btab //
T01TD1155E:196b-12: sngon chad 'khor bar sdug bsngal kun du myong gyur tshe na bdag la ni //
T01TD1155E:196b-13: gang dag yun ring ngo shes byams sems ldan pas lan brgyar grogs byas pa //
T01TD1155E:196b-14: bde ba thob tshe de dag bkol nas ji ltar yongs su spyad bya zhes //
T01TD1155E:196b-15: de slad khyod ni bdud rtsi 'ang sems can kun dang thun mong gsol bar brtson //
T01TD1155E:196b-16: mchog sbyin 'gro bar sems can rnams dang lhan cig longs spyod 'das dgongs nas //
T01TD1155E:196b-17: de dag nges par yongs su mi gtong bas na khyod kyi bstan pa ni //
T01TD1155E:196b-18: ji ltar khyod nyid ne tsor 'khrungs tshe ljon shing gzhon nu lags spyad pa'i //
T01TD1155E:196b-19: ljon shing rgas par gyur kyang yongs su mi gtong de ltar brtson pa lags //
T01TD1155E:196b-20: gang slad 'gro ba mya ngan ma 'das mya ngan khyod 'da' blo ma byung //
T01TD1155E:196b-21: bde gshegs go 'phang brnyes par nus pa ma lags de mi mdzad //
T01TD1155E:196b-22: de slad khyod ni kun mkhyen yon tan gter dag brnyes mdzad slad du brtson //
T01TD1155E:196b-23: stobs bcu'i yon tan bdag gir mdzad pa las gzhan khyod la phra mi mnga' //
T01TD1155E:196b-24: gang su la la dag gis bde gshegs go 'phang brnyes pa de dag kyang //
T01TD1155E:196b-25: 'di bas shin tu smad pa'i gnas skabs dag tu lhung ba byung ngo zhes //
T01TD1155E:197a-1: nyam ngar lhung ba'i tshe yang bdag nyid smad ma mdzad //
T01TD1155E:197a-2: bdag la smod pa mi rung skyes bu dar ba zhum par bgyid ma lags //
T01TD1155E:197a-3: gang slad gal te rang la rag las 'bad pas byang chub thob gyur na //
T01TD1155E:197a-4: sangs rgyas go 'phang rnyed dka' ma lags snyam du khyod kyi blo gros byung ;
T01TD1155E:197a-5: / de slad khyod kyis nyam nga'i dus su'ang kun mkhyen smon lam brtan bzlog pa //
T01TD1155E:197a-6: dman la dga' ba rnams kyi tshig dag khyod kyis khyad du bsad par mdzad //
T01TD1155E:197a-7: nyon mongs chu bo rab 'khrug pa dang ngan 'gro la dag rtag tu gdangs pa dang //
T01TD1155E:197a-8: so so'i skye bo'i g-yo dang sdig pa'i grogs po rtag par rgyun du gnas pa dang //
T01TD1155E:197a-9: thub rnams rnyed par dka' zhes de ltar sems zhum 'gro ba gtong ba'i rgyu //
T01TD1155E:197a-10: gang lags de nyid khyod kyi thugs rje rtag tu skye ba'i rgyur yang gyur //
T01TD1155E:197a-11: ji ltar 'gro ba rnams la khyod blo shin tu byams pa skye ba ltar //
T01TD1155E:197a-12: 'jig rten 'di dag rang la'ang byams pa'i blo gros skye bar mi 'gyur la //
T01TD1155E:197a-13: 'jig rten phongs pa'i gnas skabs gyur na bdag nyid dag kyang gtong bar bgyid //
T01TD1155E:197a-14: khyod ni shin tu nyam nga'i dus su'ang 'gro ba gtong ba bzhed ma mchis //
T01TD1155E:197a-15: gang zhig skye bo dman dang phongs pa re ba'i bsam ldan mthong na yang //
T01TD1155E:197a-16: brtse med 'bras bu 'dod pas smod gzhan yon tan dag dang ldan tshol ba //
T01TD1155E:197a-17: bsam brlag de ni sbyin pa byed kyang slong ba rnams dang mtshungs so zhes //
T01TD1155E:197a-18: de slad khyod ni thugs rjes slong ba rnams la sbyin par bzhed la zhugs //
T01TD1155E:197a-19: 'ga' zhig rang nyid ma dul bzhin du rigs par ldan pa'i tshig smra yang //
T01TD1155E:197a-20: rang gi tshig dang 'gal bar spyod pas gzhan dag 'dul bar mi nus zhes //
T01TD1155E:197a-21: khyod kyis dgongs nas de slad 'gro ba mtha' dag thugs la bzhag mdzad nas //
T01TD1155E:197a-22: re zhig bdag nyid ma dul ba nyid dul bar mdzad phyir brtson pa lags //
T01TD1155E:197a-23: gang slad mkhas pa rnams kyi mi dge'i las kyang zhi ba'i bde bar 'gyur mod kyi //
T01TD1155E:197a-24: 'on kyang 'phags pas mi dge ba dag kun du bsten 'os ma yin zhes //
T01TD1155E:197b-0: de slad khyod ni rtag tu rang bzhin yongs su dag pas sdig las log / ngan song 'jigs pas ma lags lha yi bde spyad bzhed @197b pa'i phyir ma lags //
T01TD1155E:197b-1: gang dag 'gro la mi lta bdag nyid zhi bar 'gro bar bgyi slad spyod bgyid pa //
T01TD1155E:197b-2: des kyang ci ste brtson pa ma bsten slan chad bsam rdzogs mi 'gyur na //
T01TD1155E:197b-3: gang gis 'gro ba ma lus bsgral phyir brtson pa brtsams pas ci smon zhes //
T01TD1155E:197b-4: de slad khyod kyis rang gi bde la ma gzigs byang chub slad du brtson //
T01TD1155E:197b-5: khyod kyis 'byor ba chung ba'i tshe yang sbyin par bzhed pa ma spangs la //
T01TD1155E:197b-6: bdog pa chung yang slong ba rnams la zhum mi mnga' ba'i thugs kyis stsal //
T01TD1155E:197b-7: dbang phyug chen po mnga' yang tshul dang 'gal ba'i tha snyad mi mnga' la //
T01TD1155E:197b-8: na tshod lang tshor gyur kyang 'dod pa rnams la thugs ni chags mi mnga' //
T01TD1155E:197b-9: khyod kyis thos dang blo gros che ba'i tshe na'ang bdag bstod ma mdzad la //
T01TD1155E:197b-10: 'gro ba yon tan chung ba gzhan rnams kyang ni mthon por bkur bar gyur //
T01TD1155E:197b-11: yon tan tshogs la gnas tshe nyid kyi spyod pa nyes pa chung du'ang bzung ;
T01TD1155E:197b-12: /'gro ba dmu rgod rnams la rtsol ba mi mnga' bde bar gnas pas bzhugs //
T01TD1155E:197b-13: khyod kyi thugs ni srid dang nyon mongs skyo bas zhi la dgyes gyur kyang //
T01TD1155E:197b-14: thugs rje nyid kyis mdzad pa'i yon tan skye bo rnams dang rjes su mthun //
T01TD1155E:197b-15: byed pa ma gtogs gzhan gyis 'bras bu mi myong bar ni khyod mkhyen kyang //
T01TD1155E:197b-16: 'on kyang sems can rnams kyi 'byor pa skyed slad bsod nams gter rnams bdar //
T01TD1155E:197b-17: khyod la shes rab la sogs yon tan gang dag rtag tu mnga' gyur pa //
T01TD1155E:197b-18: de dag khyod kyis 'gro ba dag gi don rnams nyid du nye bar spyad //
T01TD1155E:197b-19: de las khyod kyi bsod nams 'bras bu gzhan du mchis pa ma lags la //
T01TD1155E:197b-20: de dag 'gro ba'i 'byor slad yongs su bsngos kyang don ma mchis ma lags //
T01TD1155E:197b-21: khyod la gzhan la sman pa'i thabs dang 'bral ba'i dus 'ga' 'ang byung ma gyur //
T01TD1155E:197b-22: thabs chung ma gyur 'bras bu ma mchis ma lags 'bras bu chung ma lags //
T01TD1155E:197b-23: bsod nams chung ngu rtsom pa dag la khyod ni mngon dgyes ma lags la //
T01TD1155E:197b-24: bsod nams chu bo dag gis ngoms par ma gyur chab kyi rgya mtsho bzhin //
T01TD1155E:197b-25: mtshan mo ston ka'i zla ba nya ba'i mdangs kyis nyams dgar gyur pa dang //
T01TD1155E:198a-1: autpala rgyas pa gnyid bral mig la rngom brjid byed rnams dang //
T01TD1155E:198a-2: ri bo ljon shing me tog rgyas pa brgya yis rtse mo dkrigs rnams kyis //
T01TD1155E:198a-3: gzhan la gcig tu sman dgyes khyod kyi blo gros phrogs par rngo mi thogs //
T01TD1155E:198a-4: 'jig rten sdug bsngal dag gis smad tshe khyod ni nyid la byams pa yis //
T01TD1155E:198a-5: yul gyi dga' ba ston nyams su blang bya min zhes thugs rje'i blos mkhyen nas //
T01TD1155E:198a-6: gling bzhi'i dbang phyug mnga' yang yul rnams kyis ni thugs kyang mi phrogs la //
T01TD1155E:198a-7: khyod kyis gzhan sman lhur bzhes mdzad pas dus dag shin tu 'das par bgyis //
T01TD1155E:198a-8: phyug cing 'byor ba slong ba rnams kyis legs par spyad par ma byas dang //
T01TD1155E:198a-9: dur khrod ljon shing me tog rgyas pa'i ljid kyis g-yur za mtshungs so zhes //
T01TD1155E:198a-10: de slad bsod nams dman pa'i 'byor ba dag la slong rnams ma spyod pas //
T01TD1155E:198a-11: khyod kyi dkor nor slong ba ma mchis pa ni thugs la gcags par gyur //
T01TD1155E:198a-12: gang zhig brtse med srid pas tshong ba bzhin du 'bras bu'i phyir btsal nas //
T01TD1155E:198a-13: de ni 'bras bu yang ni slang ba rnams la sbyin par spro ma mchis //
T01TD1155E:198a-14: gang gi slad du khyod kyi gtong ba rnams dus gzhan la sman gyur pa //
T01TD1155E:198a-15: de slad de yi 'bras bu'ang slong ba rnams kyis rang gi lag par bzung //
T01TD1155E:198a-16: ri ngos ljon shing 'bras bu smin pa dag tu bya rnams lta bu dang //
T01TD1155E:198a-17: dgon pa'i rdzing bu bskyed shing bzang pos bskor bar ngal rnams ltar //
T01TD1155E:198a-18: 'dzem med slong ba dgyes pa khyod la bag phebs 'byor ba 'tshal ba yi //
T01TD1155E:198a-19: slongs mo pa dag kun nas myur bar mngon du lhags nas sdod tsing mchis //
T01TD1155E:198a-20: dpal 'byor 'bangs dang btsun mo rang gi sha dang srog kyang gtong ba na //
T01TD1155E:198a-21: khyod kyis sras gzhon rab sdug ston zla tshes pa dri med gzugs ldan pa'ang //
T01TD1155E:198a-22: slong ba rnams la gtong bar mdzad la brtson par gyur pa ji lta ba //
T01TD1155E:198a-23: de ltar gtong la goms pa khyod kyi thugs la brtan pa nyid kyang byung //
T01TD1155E:198a-24: gang zhig thos par gyur na'ang 'jig rten 'di la gnod pa skye 'gyur dang //
T01TD1155E:198b-0: gang yang khyod nyid kyis kyang yun ring sku nyams bzhes par mi @198b spyod pa'i //
T01TD1155E:198b-1: spyod pa de dag khyod la goms pas dus su rang gi ngang nyid gyur //
T01TD1155E:198b-2: de slad yon tan dag ni yongs goms ma bgyis spel bar dka' ba lags //
T01TD1155E:198b-3: ji ltar sman pa gdon gyis zin la gdon rnams bsal bar bgyid slad du //
T01TD1155E:198b-4: rdeg cing tshig rtsub smra ba spyod kyang zin pa nyid la rdeg mi bgyid //
T01TD1155E:198b-5: de ltar khyod kyang nyon mongs nyid la brtse dang bral bas spyod mdzad kyi //
T01TD1155E:198b-6: 'gro ba nyon mongs gyur pa la ni khyod nyid thugs rje mdzad pa lags //
T01TD1155E:198b-7: khyod kyis rtag tu yon tan nor lhag rnams la gus pas bsags pa mdzad //
T01TD1155E:198b-8: mnyam pa rnams la yon tan goms par bgyi slad byams pa'i thugs kyis spyad //
T01TD1155E:198b-9: dman la thugs rjes brtson pa mchog gis yon tan rnams bskrun te //
T01TD1155E:198b-10: 'gro ba rnams la khyod kyis ji ltar rigs par legs par mdzad par zhugs //
T01TD1155E:198b-11: ji ltar ma ma rang lus sna tshogs thabs tshul mang po 'dzin bgyid kyang //
T01TD1155E:198b-12: gzhon nu'i nad bsal ched lags dga' bskyed ma lags lus phyir ma lags pa //
T01TD1155E:198b-13: de ltar khyod kyang brtson pa chen pos yon tan bdag nyid bskrun mdzad pa //
T01TD1155E:198b-14: 'gro ba'i longs spyod ched lags grags dang gzhan dag zil mnan ched ma lags //
T01TD1155E:198b-15: khyod kyi blo gros gzhan la sman pa'i thabs mkhyen mdzad slad zhugs gyur pa //
T01TD1155E:198b-16: 'di ltar khyod nyid thugs rjes rnam pa de dag nyid la zhugs lags gda' //
T01TD1155E:198b-17: khyod ni brtson 'grus 'phags pas brtsal ba che yang mnyel bar ma gyur pa //
T01TD1155E:198b-18: de gsum dag gis khyod kyis gzhan sman ma bsgrubs cung zad byung ma gyur //
T01TD1155E:198b-19: khyod ni 'bad rtsol chen po can gyi phrin las mnga' bar mi bzhed la //
T01TD1155E:198b-20: spyod pa shin tu rmad du byung ba gcig tu bsam yas 'di yang byung //
T01TD1155E:198b-21: gang slad khyod kyi sems can ma mchis pa 'di thugs su chud gyur kyang //
T01TD1155E:198b-22: 'di ltar sems can don gyi slad du grangs med dus su'ang srid par bzhugs //
T01TD1155E:198b-23: gang slad shes rab don dam bstan cing snying rje kun rdzob ston mdzad pa //
T01TD1155E:198b-24: de slad don bzhin dgongs mdzad khyod la sems can mchis pa ma lags kyang //
T01TD1155E:199a-0: gang tshe khyod ni stobs bcu bskyed pa'i thugs rje dag dang ldan @199a * //
T01TD1155E:199a-2: de tshe 'gro ba nyam thag rnams la khyod byams bu la pha byams bzhin //
T01TD1155E:199a-3: 'gro ba gtugs dang nyon mongs bas pas byang chub mchog thob ma mchis la //
T01TD1155E:199a-4: nyon mongs phyogs pas rang las sman par bgyid pa'ang thob 'gyur ma lags pas //
T01TD1155E:199a-5: de slad khyod kyis byang chub brnyes slad brtson 'grus brtan pa mdzad pa na //
T01TD1155E:199a-6: nyon mongs nges par ma bsregs ran gyi dum bu bzhin du spang bar mdzad //
T01TD1155E:199a-7: khyod kyi nyon mongs dran dang mkhyen pas bzung bas yon tan sna tshogs 'grub //
T01TD1155E:199a-8: nyon mongs spang bar gyur pa byang chub rgyur yang nye bar 'gyur lags te //
T01TD1155E:199a-9: 'di ltar de yis khyod blo shol gom yul can du yang ma bgyis la //
T01TD1155E:199a-10: 'gro ba rnams su skye ba brgyud pa'ang yon tan rnams kyi zhing du mdzad //
T01TD1155E:199a-11: 'gro ba nyon mongs gyur dang sdug bsngal brgya dag byung bas bcom pa yis //
T01TD1155E:199a-12: rtsol dang bral zhing mgon ma mchis pas grang dang gang du spyod bgyid pa //
T01TD1155E:199a-13: 'gro ba de ni nyon mongs dgra thul khyod kyi thugs rjes spyod pa na //
T01TD1155E:199a-14: srid pa len dang stong dang gnas pa dag la mnga' dbang mchis pa lags //
T01TD1155E:199a-15: ci yang med pa'i skye mched kyi ni yul can phra rgyas rnams bcom nas ;
T01TD1155E:199a-16: / de dag spangs pa'i thabs tshul gang lags dam pa'i tshogs la yun ring bshad pa mdzad //
T01TD1155E:199a-17: sa gsum sman pa'i thabs mkhas mnga' ba khyod kyis phyir yang drangs nas ni //
T01TD1155E:199a-18: dud 'gro dag tu'ang smon pa mdzad nas skye ba brgya phrag rnams kyang mdzad //
T01TD1155E:199a-19: sngon gyi mi dge'i phrin las rnam par smin par ma nges gang lags pa //
T01TD1155E:199a-20: de dag dud 'gro'i 'gro bar gshegs la gzhol ba khyod la mnga' mchis pas //
T01TD1155E:199a-21: khyod kyis rnam smin ched du drangs te thugs la dgongs pa'i don bsgrubs pa //
T01TD1155E:199a-22: drang srong gis bshad gsang sngags zhi bas dug gi shugs dag bzlog pa bzhin //
T01TD1155E:199a-23: khyod kyis rtag tu mi dge'i chos dang g-yul dag spang bar gyur pa na //
T01TD1155E:199a-24: 'gro ba dar mdzad mkhas pa khyod kyis 'gro ba de dang der spyod pa'i //
T01TD1155E:199a-25: tshul khrims ma 'bad brtul zhugs ldan pa bzhin du gyur pa ji lta ba //
T01TD1155E:199b-0: de @199b ltar dam pa'i spyod lugs byang chub bsgrub pa dag la goms par mdzad //
T01TD1155E:199b-1: ma bzhin res 'ga' 'ang thugs rje dag dang ma bral mgon ma mchis rnams kyis //
T01TD1155E:199b-2: sdug bsngal de dang de dag bsal slad 'gro ba sdug bsngal can dag tu //
T01TD1155E:199b-3: bsnyengs dang bral bar spyod pa mdzad pa khyod kyi thabs la mkhas pa ni //
T01TD1155E:199b-4: bsgrub par dga' dang brnyes par dka' ba 'ga' yang byung bar ma gyur lags //
T01TD1155E:199b-5: gang slad sna tshogs thabs kyis 'gro ba sdig pa bying 'dul khyod la ni //
T01TD1155E:199b-6: dud 'gro'i 'gro ba dag kyang bde 'gro bzhin du don chen kho nar gyur //
T01TD1155E:199b-7: ngan song dag tu 'khrungs na'ang legs par spyod pa nyams pa mi mnga' ba //
T01TD1155E:199b-8: de slad khyod kyi sdig pa'ang yon tan 'gyur bar dge ba nyid dang mtshungs //
T01TD1155E:199b-9: khyod la legs brten kha cig byang chub gsum la blo gros ci rigs zhugs //
T01TD1155E:199b-10: de bzhin gzhan dag bsam gtan gzugs med dag la go 'phang gzhag pa mdzad //
T01TD1155E:199b-11: kha cig gtong bar zhugs shing nges tshul mchid kyis 'tshal gyur pas //
T01TD1155E:199b-12: khyod kyis 'jig rten dag la sman yon tan ma btags pa ni 'ga' ma mchis //
T01TD1155E:199b-13: khyod kyis 'jig rten dag na 'gro ba gang rnams nges par thar 'tshal ba //
T01TD1155E:199b-14: bde 'gror nye bar drangs shing dge ba yongs su smin pa nyid du mdzad //
T01TD1155E:199b-15: khyod kyis 'gro ba zhi mdzad slad du 'gro ba rnams su spyod pa na //
T01TD1155E:199b-16: drang srong chen po gzhan dag dus bzhin byung bas zhi bar mdzad pa bzhin //
T01TD1155E:199b-17: gang slad khyod ni 'gro ba'i skye ba bcad dang rdzogs sangs rgyas mdzad ma gtogs par //
T01TD1155E:199b-18: gzhan gyis skye ba zhi bar mi 'gyur snyam du blo gros nges gyur pa //
T01TD1155E:199b-19: de slad byung chub gzhol ba'i thugs mnga' khyod kyis srid rtse man chad kyi //
T01TD1155E:199b-20: lam rnams tshul bzhin ston par mdzad pas dus dag 'das par gyur pa lags //
T01TD1155E:199b-21: gang zhig rtogs par ma gyur pa yis 'jig rten ma rig ldongs gyur la //
T01TD1155E:199b-22: 'gro ba sdug bsngal mang por rgyu zhing 'chi bdag mtshams las mi 'da' ba'i //
T01TD1155E:199b-23: 'phags lam 'jigs med sngon gyi drang srong che rnams rjes gshegs gang lags pa //
T01TD1155E:199b-24: de ni khyod kyis 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal mthar gtugs slad du nyid kyis mkhyen //
T01TD1155E:200a-1: mtha'i tshe na nyi ma du mas chab bskams 'jig rten 'di //
T01TD1155E:200a-2: zhugs chen mched pa khros pa lta bus thal ba dag kyang sreg bgyid pa //
T01TD1155E:200a-3: de ltar dregs bral khyod kyis nyon mongs bsrabs par gyur pa'i bag chags kyang //
T01TD1155E:200a-4: ye shes zhugs chen 'ang ra ba dag gis nges par bsregs par gyur pa lags //
T01TD1155E:200a-5: gang dag sa gsum bla ma rnams la nges par gnas par 'tshal ba dag / mun pa chung ngu dang yang lhan cig gnas par 'gal ba gang lags pa'i //
T01TD1155E:200a-6: yon tan mtha' yas de dag mngon par sangs rgyas tshe na dus gcig tu //
T01TD1155E:200a-7: shing la bya rnams gnas 'cha' bzhin du gyur pa khyod kyis gang las brnyes //
T01TD1155E:200a-8: nyi ma 'od zer gsal ba stong ldan zla ba sprin dang bral gyur pa //
T01TD1155E:200a-9: lhag par dga' bar bgyid pa nam mkha'i dkyil na nges par gnas gyur kyang //
T01TD1155E:200a-10: gang gis khebs pa'i 'gro ba srid pa'i dgon pa thibs por 'khyam bgyid pa'i //
T01TD1155E:200a-11: ma rig mun nag de dag rab tu zhi ba'i thabs tshul khyod kyis bstan //
T01TD1155E:200a-12: sdug bsngal khyab pa 'di yin de rab skye bar 'gyur ba'i kun 'byung 'di //
T01TD1155E:200a-13: de mthar gtugs pa 'di yin de rtogs gyur la gzhol ba'i thabs 'di zhes //
T01TD1155E:200a-14: de ltar tshangs pa khyod kyis dag pa zla 'od gtsang ma dag kyang bstan //
T01TD1155E:200a-15: de dag rtogs bgyis skye ba dman yang tshangs pa'i go 'phang thob par 'gyur //
T01TD1155E:200a-16: ji srid nyi ma'i snang ba gang lags de ni nub kyi ri dbang gis //
T01TD1155E:200a-17: nyi ma nub par ma bgyis de srid rab rib rab tu zhi bar bgyid //
T01TD1155E:200a-18: khyod kyis skye shi mthar gtugs bgyi slad thabs tshul bstan pa gang lags pa //
T01TD1155E:200a-19: de ni khyod nyid zhi bar gshegs kyang snying gi mun nag zhi mdzad lags //
T01TD1155E:200a-20: de ltar tshangs pa'i gtso bo lha yi bla mar gyur pa tshangs gter gyis //
T01TD1155E:200a-21: bstod bgyis bstod par 'os pa bde gshegs mngon sum bzhugs bzhin bstod bgyis pas //
T01TD1155E:200a-22: bdag gi bsod nams gter dag bsags pa gang lags de yis 'gro ba rnams //
T01TD1155E:200b-0: drang srong chen po rnams kyis dgongs pa'i legs pa gang lags der gyur cig / yon tan mtha' yas par bstod pa slob dpon dkon mchog 'bangs @200b kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T01TD1155E:200b-2: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po sarba dznya de ba dang /
T01TD1155E:200b-3: lo ts'a ba bande rin chen mchog gis bsgyur /
T01TD1155E:200b-4: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba bande dpal brtsegs kyis zhus te gtan la phab pa//
